| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1022 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ece1578f-37ea-5c9e-a10d-b95f39bb402f"
